      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i keep expecting to hear his collar jingle or his paws on the floor but it’s just... nothing. i don't even know why i bother waking up anymore. the house feels too big and i just feel so heavy. i don't want to feel this weight anymore.",
